add.help:
Here are the usage for *add*:
• /add : Add yourself to the current titan queue.
• /add *element* : Add yourself to the specified titan queue.
• /add *element* *name* : (Moderator) Add a specified name to the queue.

remove.help:
Here are the usage for *remove*:
• /remove : Remove yourself from the current titan queue.
• /remove *element* : Remove yourself from the specified titan queue.
 •/remove all : Clears all queues for all titans.
• /remove *element* *number* : (Moderator) Remove a specified queue number from queue.
• /remove *element* *name* : (Moderator) Remove a specified name from the queue.
• /remove *element* all: (Moderator) Clear the queue list of specified titan.

queue.help:
Here are the usage for *queue*:
• /queue : Displays the queue for current titan.
• /queue *element* : Display the queue for the specified titan.

titan.help:
Here are the usage for *titan*:
• /titan : If the current titan right now.
• /titan *element* : (Moderator) Changes the current titan.
• /titan off : (Moderator) Sets the current titan to unknown.

clean.help:
Here are the usage for *clean*:
• /clean : (Moderator) Deletes up to 20 messages with @Miho and messages made by Miho.

info.help:
Here are the usage for *info*:
• /info *element* *name*: Displays stats for its evolution 3 level 60 version.

help.help:
Here are the usage for *Cheffenia*:
• /Cheffenia : If the current Cheffenia right now.
• /Cheffenia *element* : (Moderator) Changes the current Cheffenia.
• /Cheffenia off : (Moderator) Sets the current Cheffenia to unknown.

purge.help:
Here are the usage for *purge*:
• /purge *number*: Deletes a number of messages.
